---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Sidebar from "../components/Sidebar.astro";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Early Game Strategies - Motto Immortal</title>
</head>
<body>
  <Sidebar />

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">Early Game Strategies</h1>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <p>Welcome to Motto Immortal! This guide will help you navigate the early stages of the game and set you up for long-term success.</p>
      
      <h3>Understanding Game Progression</h3>
      <p>The game is structured in phases as you build more teams:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Early Game:</strong> Focus on building your first team (1 team)</li>
        <li><strong>Mid Game:</strong> Develop 2-3 specialized teams for different modes</li>
        <li><strong>Late Game:</strong> Build 4-5 complete teams with optimized synergies</li>
      </ul>
      <p><em>This guide focuses on the early game phase - setting your foundation for long-term success.</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>1. First Steps (Day 1-3)</h2>
      <h3>Hero Selection</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Focus on Common and Epic Heroes initially:</strong> They are easier to obtain and upgrade</li>
        <li><strong>Don't spread resources too thin:</strong> Focus on 5-6 core heroes for your main team</li>
        <li><strong>Prioritize faction bonuses:</strong> Try to build a team with 3+ heroes from the same faction</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Resource Management</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Save your gems:</strong> Only spend on guaranteed hero summons or limited events</li>
        <li><strong>Complete daily quests:</strong> They provide essential resources for progression</li>
        <li><strong>Don't rush hero upgrades:</strong> Wait until you have a clear team strategy</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>2. Building Your First Team (Day 4-7)</h2>
      <h3>Team Composition</h3>
      <p>A balanced team should include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>1-2 Tanks:</strong> To absorb damage (e.g., Ares, Athena)</li>
        <li><strong>2-3 DPS Heroes:</strong> For damage output (e.g., Zeus, Artemis)</li>
        <li><strong>1-2 Support/Healers:</strong> For sustain (e.g., Isis, Demeter)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Recommended Early Game Teams</h3>
      <div class="team-example">
        <h4>Budget Team (Common/Epic Focus)</h4>
        <p>Ares (Tank) ‚Ä¢ Artemis (DPS) ‚Ä¢ Athena (Tank/Support) ‚Ä¢ Heracles (DPS) ‚Ä¢ Isis (Healer)</p>
      </div>

      <h3>Priority Heroes by Role</h3>
      <p><strong>Start with heroes from these categories for best results:</strong></p>
      
      <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Frontliners (Tank/Warrior)</h4>
      <p>Build these tanks first for stable team defense:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Poseidon, Momus, Jormungandr, Hladgunnr</li>
        <li>Prometheus, Khepri, Set</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h4>‚öîÔ∏è Damage Dealers (Archer/Assassin/Mage)</h4>
      <p>These heroes provide consistent damage output:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Isis, Hecate, Nemesis, Hladgunnr (also warrior)</li>
        <li>Jingwei, Bastet, Anubis, Phoenix</li>
        <li>Hela</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h4>‚ú® Support Heroes</h4>
      <p>Provide buffs and utility for your team:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tefnut, Caishen, Pan, Yuelao</li>
        <li>Athena, Set, Cancer, Aquarius</li>
        <li>Diana</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Star Heroes as Base Copies</h3>
      <p><strong>If you obtain Star Heroes early, these are excellent to start with:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>‚úÖ <strong>Nuwa, Amun Ra, Nyx, Dio</strong> - Good at base copy (Legendary)</li>
        <li>‚ö†Ô∏è <strong>Zeus, Nezha</strong> - Require heavy investment to be effective</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Powerful Team Synergies to Build Toward</h3>
      <div class="team-example">
        <h4>Synergy Combinations</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Isis / Jingwei + Caishen:</strong> Strong damage amplification combo</li>
          <li><strong>Hladgunnr + Yuelao + Hecate:</strong> Balanced offense and defense</li>
          <li><strong>Nuwa + Assassins + Tefnut:</strong> Burst damage team with utility</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>3. Progression Tips (Week 1-2)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Push Campaign as far as possible:</strong> This unlocks more game modes and idle rewards</li>
        <li><strong>Join an active guild:</strong> Guild benefits are crucial for progression</li>
        <li><strong>Participate in events:</strong> They often provide exclusive rewards</li>
        <li><strong>Focus on the Shrine:</strong> Upgrading shrine bonuses benefits your entire roster</li>
        <li><strong>Complete Tower daily:</strong> Great source of hero shards and upgrade materials</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>4. Important Focus Areas (F2P / Low Spender)</h2>
      <div class="warning-box">
        <h3>If you're F2P or a low spender, remember:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Focus on <strong>one strong team</strong> before expanding</li>
          <li>Prioritize the heroes listed above - they're efficient investments</li>
          <li>Common and Epic heroes can carry you through early game</li>
          <li>Save your limited resources (gems, tokens) carefully</li>
          <li>Don't rush - legendary heroes will come with patience</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <h2>5. Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
      <div class="warning-box">
        <ul>
          <li>Upgrading too many heroes at once</li>
          <li>Neglecting faction synergies</li>
          <li>Wasting gems on random summons</li>
          <li>Ignoring the Shrine upgrades</li>
          <li>Not joining a guild early</li>
          <li>Missing daily login rewards</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card">
      <h2>6. Mid-Game Transition (Week 3+)</h2>
      <p>As you progress, start focusing on:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Legendary Heroes:</strong> Begin working toward specific legendary heroes</li>
        <li><strong>Team Synergies:</strong> Build compositions around specific strategies</li>
        <li><strong>Relic Upgrades:</strong> Don't neglect hero relics, they provide significant power boosts</li>
        <li><strong>PvP Arena:</strong> Start competing for better rewards and rankings</li>
        <li><strong>Event Optimization:</strong> Plan your resources around major events</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="content-card tips-card">
      <h2>Pro Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Save event currency for the most valuable rewards</li>
        <li>Use the hero tier list to guide your investments</li>
        <li>Watch content creators for advanced strategies</li>
        <li>Be patient - this is an idle game, progress takes time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
/* RESET & BASE */
html, body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-family: "Spectral", "Roboto", system-ui, sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% -10%, rgba(120,90,200,0.15), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(255,215,100,0.08), transparent 55%),
    linear-gradient(to bottom, #0d0b10, #07060c);
  color: #e6e6eb;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

/* PAGE LAYOUT WITH SIDEBAR */
body {
  margin-left: 80px;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  body {
    margin-left: 0;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
}

/* HERO SECTION */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  height: 320px;
  background-image: url("/bg.jpg");
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center;
  background-attachment: fixed;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 60%;
  background: linear-gradient(
    to top,
    rgba(7, 6, 12, 0.95) 0%,
    rgba(7, 6, 12, 0.7) 40%,
    transparent 100%
  );
  pointer-events: none;
}

.hero-headline {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  padding: 0 32px 32px;
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #fff;
  text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero {
    height: 240px;
  }
  
  .hero-headline {
    font-size: 2rem;
    padding: 0 24px 24px;
  }
}

/* MAIN CONTENT */
.main-content {
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 32px 80px;
}

.content-card {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}

.content-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5);
}

.content-card h2 {
  margin-top: 0;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-size: 2rem;
  color: #fcd34d;
  border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.3);
  padding-bottom: 12px;
}

.content-card h3 {
  margin-top: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  color: #fcd34d;
}

.content-card h4 {
  margin-top: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  color: #e6e6eb;
}

.content-card p {
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: #e6e6eb;
}

.content-card ul {
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: #e6e6eb;
}

.content-card li {
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.content-card strong {
  color: #e6e6eb;
}

.team-example {
  background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
  border-left: 4px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.6);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 16px 0;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.team-example h4 {
  margin-top: 0;
  color: #fcd34d;
}

.team-example p {
  margin-bottom: 0;
  font-family: monospace;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #e6e6eb;
}

.warning-box {
  background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1);
  border-left: 4px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.6);
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin: 16px 0;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.warning-box ul {
  margin: 0;
}

.tips-card {
  background: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.4);
}

.tips-card h2 {
  color: #fcd34d;
  border-bottom-color: rgba(250, 204, 21, 0.4);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .content-card {
    padding: 24px 20px;
  }

  .content-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
}
</style>
